casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Sanchez, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Sanchez (2000), 88 Ohio St.3d 16.]

(No. 99-998 Submitted December 14, 1999 Decided February 9, 2000.) Thomas L. Sartini, Ashtabula County Prosecuting Attorney, and Ariana E. Tarighati, Chief Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant.

The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed on the authority of State v. Dye (1998), 82 Ohio St.3d 323, 695 N.E.2d 763.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
